<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5235459>
    dc:description "Figures 2A-K. Desmopachria carranca. (A) Dorsal View. (B) Colour pattern of elytron. (C) Ventral view. (D-K) Male genitalia. (D) Dorsal view. (E) Ventral view. (F) Lateral view. (G) Coverslip dorsal view. (H) Lateral lobe dorsal view. (I) Median lobe dorsal view. (J) Median lobe lateral view. (K) Lateral lobe lateral view. Figs.2A-C scale bars = 1 mm,Figs.2D-K scale bars= 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5235459/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

